8. Monitoring and Visibility

Security depends heavily on logging and visibility.

Beginner Questions

• How do I enable Microsoft 365 audit logging?
• Where do I view security alerts?
• How do I monitor user login activity?
• What logs should always be enabled?

Intermediate Questions

• What is Microsoft Sentinel?
• How do I export Microsoft 365 logs to a SIEM?
• How do I detect suspicious sign-ins?

