9. External Collaboration

External collaboration introduces risk if not controlled.

Beginner Questions

• How do I manage guest users in Microsoft 365?
• Should guest users be required to use MFA?
• How do I disable anonymous file sharing?

Intermediate Questions

• How do I restrict external sharing in SharePoint?
• How do I audit guest user activity?

