10. Security Incident Response

Security teams must be prepared for compromise.

Beginner Questions

• What should I do if a Microsoft 365 account is compromised?
• How do I revoke user sessions?
• How do I reset a compromised account securely?

Intermediate Questions

• How do I investigate suspicious sign-ins?
• How do I trace malicious email messages?

Advanced Questions

• How do I respond to data exfiltration incidents?
• What is the Microsoft 365 incident response workflow?

